    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1077895186596553283.description1":"&7Summons a &5Possessed Elder Guardian&7 that drops &62–4 Nautilus Shells&7 and has a &640%% chance&7 to drop a &1Heart of the Sea&7.  ",
