    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3767427217424758774.description1":"&7Soul Gems &7allow you to move mobs while keeping all of their &cNBT&7 intact.  ",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3767427217424758774.description2":"&7They’re especially useful for transporting creatures to &5Rituals &7for sacrifice.",
